extends ../layouts/modern-layout

block layout-content
  br
  // Hero Section
  section.bg-gradient-primary.py-5
    .container
      .row.align-items-center
        .col-lg-10.mx-auto.text-center
          h1.display-4.fw-bold.mb-3
            i.bi.bi-robot.me-3
            | Azure DevOps Wiki Expert GPT
          h2.h3.mb-4 Accelerate Azure DevOps Wiki Writing with AI
          p.lead.mb-5
            | Discover how Azure Wiki Expert GPT automates content generation in Markdown format, ensuring fast, efficient, and consistent documentation for your DevOps workflows.

          .text-center.mb-4
            a.btn.btn-warning.btn-lg(
              href='https://chatgpt.com/g/g-KyB0DETFV-azure-wiki-expert'
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            )
              i.bi.bi-lightning-charge.me-2
              | Try Azure Wiki Expert GPT
              i.bi.bi-box-arrow-up-right.ms-2

  // Main Article Content
  article#main-article
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-8.mx-auto

          // Table of Contents
          nav#table-of-contents.mb-5(aria-label='Table of Contents')
            .card.bg-light
              .card-header
                h3.card-title.mb-0.fw-bold
                  i.bi.bi-list-ul.me-2
                  | Table of Contents
              .card-body
                ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                  li.list-group-item: a.text-decoration-none(href='#introduction') Introduction to AI-Powered Documentation
                  li.list-group-item: a.text-decoration-none(href='#azure-devops-overview') Azure DevOps Wiki Overview
                  li.list-group-item: a.text-decoration-none(href='#wiki-expert-features') Azure Wiki Expert GPT Features
                  li.list-group-item: a.text-decoration-none(href='#key-benefits') Key Benefits and Use Cases
                  li.list-group-item: a.text-decoration-none(href='#getting-started') Getting Started Guide
                  li.list-group-item: a.text-decoration-none(href='#conclusion') Conclusion and Next Steps

          // Introduction Section
          section#introduction.mb-5
            .card.shadow-sm.border-0
              .card-header.bg-success.text-white
                h2.h3.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-file-text.me-2
                  | Introduction to AI-Powered Documentation
              .card-body
                p.mb-4
                  | Writing documentation is a crucial part of any software development process. As someone who frequently writes Azure DevOps wiki pages to document best practices and functionality overviews, I know how time-consuming this task can be.

                .alert.alert-info.border-0.shadow-sm.mb-4
                  .d-flex.align-items-start
                    i.bi.bi-lightbulb.text-info.me-3.fs-4
                    div
                      h4.alert-heading.h6.mb-2 The Solution
                      p.mb-0
                        | That's why I developed the Azure Wiki Expert GPT hosted on ChatGPT.com. This tool has significantly streamlined the documentation process by leveraging advanced AI capabilities.

                p.mb-0
                  | By automating content generation and ensuring consistency across documentation, Azure Wiki Expert GPT allows your team to focus on refining and enhancing the quality of your DevOps documentation rather than starting from scratch every time.

            a(href='#table-of-contents' class='d-block mb-4 text-decoration-none')
              i.bi.bi-arrow-up-circle.me-1
              | Back to Top

          // Azure DevOps Wiki Overview Section
          section#azure-devops-overview.mb-5
            h2.h3.text-primary.mb-4
              i.bi.bi-journal-code.me-2
              | Azure DevOps Wiki Overview

            .card.shadow-sm.border-0.mb-4
              .card-header.bg-primary.text-white
                h3.h5.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-gear.me-2
                  | Key Uses of Azure DevOps Wiki
              .card-body
                .row.g-3
                  .col-md-6
                    .card.border-primary.h-100
                      .card-body
                        h4.card-title.h6
                          i.bi.bi-file-earmark-text.me-2
                          | Documentation
                        ul.card-text.small.mb-0
                          li Project Documentation: Requirements, design documents, technical specifications
                          li Process Documentation: SOPs, workflows, development practices

                  .col-md-6
                    .card.border-success.h-100
                      .card-body
                        h4.card-title.h6
                          i.bi.bi-share.me-2
                          | Knowledge Sharing
                        ul.card-text.small.mb-0
                          li Team Knowledge Base: Troubleshooting guides, FAQs, best practices
                          li Training Material: Onboarding, tutorials, training resources

                  .col-md-6
                    .card.border-warning.h-100
                      .card-body
                        h4.card-title.h6
                          i.bi.bi-people.me-2
                          | Collaboration
                        ul.card-text.small.mb-0
                          li Meeting Notes: Minutes, action items, decisions
                          li Project Planning: Plans, roadmaps, milestones

                  .col-md-6
                    .card.border-info.h-100
                      .card-body
                        h4.card-title.h6
                          i.bi.bi-graph-up.me-2
                          | Tracking & Reporting
                        ul.card-text.small.mb-0
                          li Sprint Documentation: Goals, retrospectives, reviews
                          li Release Notes: Version logs and updates

            .accordion#best-practices-accordion.mb-4
              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#bestPracticesHeading
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#bestPracticesCollapse'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='bestPracticesCollapse'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-star.me-2
                    | Best Practices for Azure DevOps Wiki
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#bestPracticesCollapse(
                  aria-labelledby='bestPracticesHeading'
                  data-bs-parent='#best-practices-accordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    .row.g-3
                      .col-md-6
                        h4.h6.text-primary Structure & Organization
                        ul.small
                          li Hierarchical Organization: Logical content structure
                          li Consistent Naming Conventions: Standardized page names

                      .col-md-6
                        h4.h6.text-success Content Management
                        ul.small
                          li Version Control: Track changes and maintain history
                          li Regular Updates: Keep content current and relevant

                      .col-md-6
                        h4.h6.text-warning Formatting & Presentation
                        ul.small
                          li Markdown: Use proper formatting standards
                          li Templates: Create reusable content structures

                      .col-md-6
                        h4.h6.text-info Collaboration & Accessibility
                        ul.small
                          li Permissions: Control access appropriately
                          li Feedback Mechanism: Enable team input and reviews

            .card.bg-light.mb-4
              .card-header
                h4.h6.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-link-45deg.me-2
                  | Learn More About Azure DevOps Wiki
              .card-body
                .row.g-2
                  .col-md-12
                    a.btn.btn-outline-primary.btn-sm(href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/devops/project/wiki/?view=azure-devops" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                      i.bi.bi-file-earmark-text.me-1
                      | Microsoft Docs: Azure DevOps Wiki
                  .col-md-6
                    a.btn.btn-outline-secondary.btn-sm(href="https://www.devopsgroup.com/insights/blogs/using-azure-devops-wiki/" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                      i.bi.bi-journal.me-1
                      | DevOpsGroup Guide
                  .col-md-6
                    a.btn.btn-outline-info.btn-sm(href="https://medium.com/@sarahamann/best-practices-for-using-azure-devops-wiki-4f948a534bf7" target="_blank" rel="noopener")
                      i.bi.bi-medium.me-1
                      | Medium Best Practices

            a(href='#table-of-contents' class='d-block mb-4 text-decoration-none')
              i.bi.bi-arrow-up-circle.me-1
              | Back to Top

          // Wiki Expert Features Section
          section#wiki-expert-features.mb-5
            h2.h3.text-primary.mb-4
              i.bi.bi-cpu.me-2
              | Azure Wiki Expert GPT Features

            .text-center.mb-4
              .card.shadow-sm
                .card-body
                  img.img-fluid.rounded(
                    src='/assets/img/MarkHazleton-AzureWikiExpertGPT.png'
                    alt='Azure Wiki Expert GPT Interface'
                    title='Azure Wiki Expert GPT'
                  )
                  .mt-3
                    a.btn.btn-primary(
                      href='https://chatgpt.com/g/g-KyB0DETFV-azure-wiki-expert'
                      target='_blank'
                      rel='noopener'
                    )
                      i.bi.bi-chat-dots.me-2
                      | Launch Azure Wiki Expert GPT

            p.lead.mb-4
              | The Azure Wiki Expert GPT, hosted on ChatGPT.com, is designed to simplify the creation of Azure DevOps wiki pages. Leveraging the power of GPT-4o, this tool helps you kickstart your wiki articles, making the documentation process more efficient and less error-prone.

            .row.g-4.mb-4
              .col-md-6
                .card.border-primary.h-100
                  .card-header.bg-primary.text-white
                    h3.h6.mb-0
                      i.bi.bi-code-square.me-2
                      | Azure DevOps Markdown Format
                  .card-body
                    p.card-text.small
                      | One of the standout features is the ability to generate Azure DevOps Markdown-ready content. Azure DevOps has unique markup requirements, such as Mermaid diagrams and table of contents tags. Azure Wiki Expert GPT understands these nuances, ensuring your documentation adheres to these standards right from the start.

              .col-md-6
                .card.border-success.h-100
                  .card-header.bg-success.text-white
                    h3.h6.mb-0
                      i.bi.bi-magic.me-2
                      | Automated Content Generation
                  .card-body
                    p.card-text.small
                      | The tool's ability to generate content automatically is incredibly beneficial. Whether you need an overview of new functionality or best practices for a specific process, Azure Wiki Expert GPT provides a solid starting point while ensuring consistency across your documentation.

              .col-md-6
                .card.border-warning.h-100
                  .card-header.bg-warning.text-dark
                    h3.h6.mb-0
                      i.bi.bi-sliders.me-2
                      | Customizability and Flexibility
                  .card-body
                    p.card-text.small
                      | Despite its advanced capabilities, Azure Wiki Expert GPT offers a high degree of customizability. You can easily tweak the generated content to better suit your specific needs, making it a flexible tool for a variety of documentation tasks.

              .col-md-6
                .card.border-info.h-100
                  .card-header.bg-info.text-white
                    h3.h6.mb-0
                      i.bi.bi-speedometer2.me-2
                      | Improved Productivity
                  .card-body
                    p.card-text.small
                      | By automating the initial stages of documentation, Azure Wiki Expert GPT allows you to focus on refining and improving content. This results in higher-quality documentation and improved productivity, freeing up time for other critical tasks.

            a(href='#table-of-contents' class='d-block mb-4 text-decoration-none')
              i.bi.bi-arrow-up-circle.me-1
              | Back to Top

          // Key Benefits Section
          section#key-benefits.mb-5
            h2.h3.text-primary.mb-4
              i.bi.bi-trophy.me-2
              | Key Benefits and Use Cases

            .card.shadow-sm.border-0
              .card-header.bg-warning.text-dark
                h3.h5.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-building.me-2
                  | Tangible Benefits for Businesses
              .card-body
                p.mb-4
                  | Ultimately, the goal of any documentation tool is to deliver tangible benefits for the business. Azure Wiki Expert GPT achieves this by making the documentation process more efficient, ensuring that best practices and functionality overviews are documented accurately and consistently.

                .alert.alert-success.border-0.shadow-sm.mb-4
                  .d-flex.align-items-start
                    i.bi.bi-check-circle.text-success.me-3.fs-4
                    div
                      h4.alert-heading.h6.mb-2 Business Impact
                      p.mb-0
                        | This leads to better-informed teams, more streamlined workflows, and reduced time-to-market for documentation deliverables.

                .row.g-3
                  .col-md-4
                    .card.border-primary.text-center
                      .card-body
                        i.bi.bi-clock.text-primary.fs-1.mb-3
                        h5.card-title Time Savings
                        p.card-text.small Reduce documentation creation time by up to 70%

                  .col-md-4
                    .card.border-success.text-center
                      .card-body
                        i.bi.bi-shield-check.text-success.fs-1.mb-3
                        h5.card-title Quality Assurance
                        p.card-text.small Ensure consistent formatting and structure across all docs

                  .col-md-4
                    .card.border-info.text-center
                      .card-body
                        i.bi.bi-people-fill.text-info.fs-1.mb-3
                        h5.card-title Team Efficiency
                        p.card-text.small Enable teams to focus on high-value content refinement

            a(href='#table-of-contents' class='d-block mb-4 text-decoration-none')
              i.bi.bi-arrow-up-circle.me-1
              | Back to Top

          // Getting Started Section
          section#getting-started.mb-5
            h2.h3.text-primary.mb-4
              i.bi.bi-play-circle.me-2
              | Getting Started Guide

            .card.shadow-sm.border-0
              .card-header.bg-info.text-white
                h3.h5.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-rocket.me-2
                  | Quick Start Steps
              .card-body
                .row.g-3
                  .col-md-6
                    .card.border-success
                      .card-body
                        h4.card-title.h6
                          span.badge.bg-success.me-2 1
                          | Access the Tool
                        p.card-text.small
                          | Visit the Azure Wiki Expert GPT on ChatGPT.com using the link provided above.

                  .col-md-6
                    .card.border-warning
                      .card-body
                        h4.card-title.h6
                          span.badge.bg-warning.text-dark.me-2 2
                          | Describe Your Needs
                        p.card-text.small
                          | Provide details about the documentation you need, including topic, audience, and scope.

                  .col-md-6
                    .card.border-info
                      .card-body
                        h4.card-title.h6
                          span.badge.bg-info.me-2 3
                          | Review Generated Content
                        p.card-text.small
                          | Examine the AI-generated Markdown content and structure provided by the tool.

                  .col-md-6
                    .card.border-primary
                      .card-body
                        h4.card-title.h6
                          span.badge.bg-primary.me-2 4
                          | Customize and Deploy
                        p.card-text.small
                          | Refine the content to match your specific requirements and deploy to your Azure DevOps wiki.

            a(href='#table-of-contents' class='d-block mb-4 text-decoration-none')
              i.bi.bi-arrow-up-circle.me-1
              | Back to Top

  // Conclusion Section
  section#conclusion.mb-5
    .card.border-primary.shadow-sm
      .card-header.bg-primary.text-white
        h2.h3.mb-0
          i.bi.bi-check-circle.me-2
          | Conclusion and Next Steps
      .card-body
        p.lead.mb-4
          | The Azure Wiki Expert GPT hosted on ChatGPT.com is an invaluable addition to any documentation toolkit. It addresses the unique challenges of Azure DevOps Markdown, automates content generation, and offers customizability that makes it suitable for a wide range of documentation needs.

        .alert.alert-success.border-0.shadow-sm.mb-4
          .d-flex.align-items-start
            i.bi.bi-star-fill.text-success.me-3.fs-4
            div
              h4.alert-heading.h6.mb-2 Ready to Transform Your Documentation Process?
              p.mb-0
                | If you're looking to improve your documentation process and boost team productivity, Azure Wiki Expert GPT provides the AI-powered assistance you need to create professional, consistent documentation efficiently.

        .text-center.mb-4
          a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg(
            href='https://chatgpt.com/g/g-KyB0DETFV-azure-wiki-expert'
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          )
            i.bi.bi-rocket.me-2
            | Get Started with Azure Wiki Expert GPT
            i.bi.bi-arrow-right.ms-2

        p.mb-0
          | Experience the difference that AI-powered documentation can make for your Azure DevOps workflows. Try Azure Wiki Expert GPT today and discover how it can streamline your documentation process while maintaining the high standards your team demands.

